{"type":"message","id":"e28fa02f","parentId":"9749c4ab","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:10:43.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - the session_status shows 21% context usage (41k/200k), but the context-monitor script shows 76% (152425/200000 tokens). This discrepancy might be because the monitor script is reading different metrics.\n\nWait, the session_status shows \"Context: 41k/200k (21%)\" which is quite low. But the monitor script shows \"Context usage: 76% (152425/200000 tokens)\". \n\nThe monitor script says \"totalTokens / contextTokens\" which might be a different metric. The session_status shows totalTokens=603 and contextTokens=218. But the monitor shows used=152425, total=200000.\n\nThese are likely measuring different things. The session_status shows current request context (603 in / 218 out), while the monitor script might be showing cumulative or total allocated context.\n\nLooking at the monitor output again: 152425/200000 tokens - that's 76%. But session_status shows 21% (41k/200k). \n\nHmm, actually 41k/200k = 20.5%, not 21%. And the session_status says \"Context: 41k/200k (21%)\". So 41k is the current context usage.\n\nThe monitor script says 152425 totalTokens. But session_status shows only 603 tokens in the current request. So totalTokens in the monitor might mean something else - perhaps the total tokens used in the session history or something.\n\nLet me look at this more carefully. The monitor script says:\n- used = $mainSession.totalTokens = 152425\n- total = $mainSession.contextTokens = 200000\n- usage = 76%\n\nWhile session_status shows:\n- Context: 41k/200k (21%)\n\nThese are definitely measuring different things. The session_status \"Context\" is the current context window usage (41k out of 200k = 21%). \n\nThe monitor's totalTokens likely represents the cumulative tokens consumed throughout the session rather than the current context window. Since the current context is only at 21%, there's no need to switch sessions - we're well within safe limits.","thinkingSignature":"ad9164fed240f7fac769014eaf899dea9c067a356d2a385c36bf87cc0e77d6cf"},{"type":"text","text":"**Context Monitor 结果**\n\n当前监控结果：会话上下文 **21%**（41k/200k tokens），运行正常，无需切换。\n\n监控脚本报告的 76% 是 `totalTokens`（历史累计消耗），而 session_status 显示的 21% 才是当前上下文实际使用量，二者指标不同。\n\n📊 **当前状态**：一切正常，继续使用即可。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4545,"output":522,"cacheRead":37004,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42071,"cost":{"input":0.0018180000000000002,"output":0.0007830000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0014801600000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00408116}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773933029659}}
